title: Educator.com - General Biology with Bryan Cardella
description: Professor Bryan Cardella covers everything in biology from the microscopic to the macroscopic. This course is perfect for both high school and college students beginning their journey into biology, or just needing a quick refresher. Bryan explains all concepts in easy to understand chunks complete with tons of diagrams and drawings. The course covers everything from Cells and DNA, through Evolution, Plants, Ecology, and even in-depth overviews of common Labs. Professor Cardella brings both extensive knowledge and engaging delivery with his 5+ years teaching life sciences and stand-up comedy experience.
